Made this #warhammer40k desert scape wargaming table for my husband for his bday

@peculiarbeautybar is owned by Taylar who loves horror, oddities and making others feel relaxed and beautiful. The studio is decorated in curiosities and witchy art, all lit by neon mood lighting. It’s definitely a vibe and all the facials are named about famous songs! I received the ‘Most Dope’ CBD Dermaplane Facial named after Mac Miller. 

This treatment includes: 
Double Cleanse 
Dermaplaning 
Extractions 
CBD Hydrojelly Mask 
Customized CBD Boosters 
+ Face/Shoulder/Décolleté Massage

Check out @peculiarbeautybar on South Tacoma Way, which also happens to be neighbors with other local favorites like @howdybagel and @buddyschickenandwaffles ✨
